01:38.423 --> 01:41.787
And who might you be?

01:46.524 --> 01:49.629
[clicking]

01:52.101 --> 01:54.234
<i>[theme music playing]</i>

02:54.768 --> 02:57.127
<b>2x09 - Homecoming</b>

03:03.453 --> 03:06.529
